            <bug_when>2010-01-18 14:58:05 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>At the moment the browsers do not mention if the scroll direction is vertical 
or horizontal... The ScrollArea checks if an vertical scrollbar is visible and 
then scrolls vertical or checks for a horizontal scrollbar and then scroll 
horizontally. This means that it is always scrolled vertically if both 
scrollbars are visible.

We can not fix this bug at the moment.</thetext>
